{"tid":2019673,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"沈旭暉：親共分子明知國際對納粹政權極具討論空間 卻故意說謊跟隨主旋律","createTime":"2020-05-16T12:29:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-16T14:13:39.000Z","uid":21470,"like":41,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ee5b9406baab48b6d360b444ab9716dfc295d121","tid":2019673,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T12:29:04.000Z","msg":"堅離地城：沈旭暉國際生活台 Simon's Glos World<br />\n<br />\n世上不是只有DSE。IGCSE (國際中學教育普通證書)由劍橋大學創立，作為全球14-16歲學生的國際普通中學教育認證，全球大多數大學、僱主普遍承認。IGCSE 對納粹政權極具討論空間。日後全球大學、僱主怎樣看待DSE？<br />\n<br />\n最失望的是，居然有外國畢業的朋友跟隨主旋律大聲疾呼「英國不會這樣出題」、「德國不會這樣出題」、「美國不會這樣出題」，而其實英國德國美國，偏偏就是這樣出題，而我不相信他們真的不知道。人間百態，盡在2020文革2.0。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5vZBuYg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5vZBuYg.jpg&h=2c0d3f48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo/?fbid=3265787150122079&amp;set=a.224514904249334\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto%2F%3Ffbid%3D3265787150122079%26set%3Da.224514904249334&d=IqGrl%2FmL2I6%2Fp6gKwmVM%2BSPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=eba1a85d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo/?fbid=3265787150122079&amp;set=a.224514904249334</a>"},{"pid":"6c0b1e2b0182cb2e18c0e52344d5c1c83e805bda","tid":2019673,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T12:29:54.000Z","msg":"延伸閱讀<br />\n「香港文革2.0」批鬥歷史試題，與「中國文革1.0」批鬥海瑞罷官<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=39J-zgGp0Gk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D39J-zgGp0Gk&d=IqGrl%2FmL2I6%2Fp6gKwmVM%2BSPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=39f9f5fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=39J-zgGp0Gk</a>"},{"pid":"14645a380cae1ee384a3a8fa96970f52c60f4ae0","tid":2019673,"uid":24345,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T12:31:24.000Z","msg":"尋日打好多字話DSE嗰題不道德乜乜乜嗰啲撚樣去曬邊"},{"pid":"4fc8588c9